FBIS4-54527 "dreeu084_p_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 POLAND Further Reportage on Continuing Strikes Further Reportage on Continuing Strikes Solidarity Leader on Pawlak's Speech LD2904140494 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1321 GMT 29 Apr 94 LD2904140494 Warsaw PAP Polish BFN [Text] Katowice, 29 Apr--During a meeting of Solidarity's National Protest Action Staff in Jastrzebie, Katowice Province, on 29 April, Solidarity leader Marian Krzaklewski said that Prime Minister Waldemar Pawlak's report to the Sejm on the situation in the country was "vague and confrontational, and contained many untruths."
